languages.text: В мешанине из приборов и коммуникаций заметны устройства буквально из разных эпох — древние, просто старинные, и наскоро сделанные современные.

traits.locale_text: [Draft] Тут встречаются элементы как археотечные, сделнные тысячи лет назад, так и современные

languages.text: In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.
languages.original_text: В мешанине из приборов и коммуникаций заметны устройства буквально из разных эпох — древние, просто старинные, и наскоро сделанные современные.

traits.locale_text: In this mishmash of devices and communications, you notice equipment virtually from different eras — ancient, simply old, and hastily tossed together modern.
In this mishmash of devices and communications, you notice equipment virtually from different eras — ancient, simply old, and hastily tossed together modern.
In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.

In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.

languages.text: 无数设备与电缆混杂在一起。你注意到，这些乱七八糟的设备来自不同的时代。有些设备非常古老，有些设备只是有些老旧，还有些设备是最近几年才被捣鼓出来的。
languages.original_text: In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.

traits.locale_text: 无数设备与电缆混杂在一起。你注意到，这些乱七八糟的设备来自不同的时代。有些设备非常古老，有些设备只是有些老旧，还有些设备是最近几年才被捣鼓出来的。

languages.text: Entre este revoltijo de aparatos y cables puedes observar equipo de eras totalmente dispares: algunos los considerarías arcaicos; otros, simplemente antiguos, y otros han sido montados apresuradamente en épocas más recientes.
languages.original_text: In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.

traits.locale_text: Entre este revoltijo de aparatos y cables puedes observar equipo de eras totalmente dispares: algunos los considerarías arcaicos; otros, simplemente antiguos, y otros han sido montados apresuradamente en épocas más recientes.

languages.text: ケーブルやら機械やらでゴチャゴチャしたソレは、全く異なる時代の装置の寄せ集めのようだ…古代のもの、少し古いもの、近年せっせと組み立てられたものと、様々だ。
languages.original_text: In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.

traits.locale_text: ケーブルやら機械やらでゴチャゴチャしたソレは、全く異なる時代の装置の寄せ集めのようだ…古代のもの、少し古いもの、近年せっせと組み立てられたものと、様々だ。

languages.text: Du bemerkst in diesem Wirrwarr von Geräten und Kabeln Ausrüstung aus verschiedensten Zeiten – manches uralt, einiges lediglich alt und anderes in neueren Jahren hastig zusammengebaut.
languages.original_text: In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.

traits.locale_text: Du bemerkst in diesem Wirrwarr von Geräten und Kabeln Ausrüstung aus verschiedensten Zeiten – manches uralt, einiges lediglich alt und anderes in neueren Jahren hastig zusammengebaut.

languages.text: Au milieu de ce capharnaüm d'appareils et de câbles, vous remarquez des pièces d'équipement issues d'époques très différentes : quelques antiquités, du matériel simplement un peu âgé, mais aussi d'autres éléments plus récents assemblés à la va-vite.
languages.original_text: In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.

traits.locale_text: Au milieu de ce capharnaüm d'appareils et de câbles, vous remarquez des pièces d'équipement issues d'époques très différentes : quelques antiquités, du matériel simplement un peu âgé, mais aussi d'autres éléments plus récents assemblés à la va-vite.

languages.text: Bu kablo ve cihaz karmaşasının içinde apayrı çağlardan kalma ekipmanlar görüyorsun. Bazıları resmen tarih öncesi iken, birkaçıysa eski sayılır. Geri kalanlarsa geçtiğimiz senelerde alelacele bir araya getirilmiş.
languages.original_text: In this mishmash of devices and cables, you notice equipment from totally different eras — some ancient, some merely old, and others hastily tossed together in more recent years.

traits.locale_text: Bu kablo ve cihaz yığınının içinde apayrı çağlardan kalma ekipmanlar görüyorsun. Bazıları çok eski, birkaçı eski sayılır, diğerleriyse geçtiğimiz yıllardan kalma ve aceleyle bir araya getirilmiş.
